data.description: Charming Dollhouse Alert! Step into the enchanting world of 714 N Washington St, Rome, NY – where every detail is as adorable as a dollhouse! This delightful property is a unique blend of coziness and character. This classic Victorian dollhouse is a true gem, boasting timeless elegance, ample space, and modern comforts. The spacious living areas feature intricate woodwork, soaring ceilings, and large windows that flood the rooms with natural light. The first floor offers versatile spaces, including a potential 6th bedroom that could serve as a home office or guest room. Come see it for yourself and receive a pleasant surprise of the large, open attic with a full bathroom and 3 rooms. Step outside into your own private paradise with a fully fenced-in yard, serene stone patio and on warm summer days, take a dip in the above-ground pool. If that's not enough- you also have a full finished basement with a fireplace! Don't miss the opportunity to make this Victorian dollhouse your forever home. Schedule a showing today and experience the magic of 714 N Washington St, Rome, NY 13440. This is a once-in-a-lifetime chance to own a piece of history with all the modern comforts you desire!
